{"tid":1396952,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"[罷食] 黃大仙竹園茶記侍應：用子彈射死佢地就岩","createTime":"2019-08-02T09:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T13:32:36.000Z","uid":296900,"like":25,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c5aee0df57496155f37a42ef4c2c15b45ce53b","tid":1396952,"uid":296900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"P牌終於開到acc可能會1999<br />\n<br />\n事源今日同女朋友去食下午茶<br />\n我地兩個因為都唔係話好精神所以就冇咩吹水<br />\n靜靜地自己係電話睇新聞間唔中講兩句<br />\n我地好細聲話 工聯會好廢 張建宗乜乜乜<br />\n<br />\n點知個女侍應一路行過偷聽<br />\n跟住同d伙計講<br />\n佢地就開始大大聲講新聞<br />\n話警察好野拉倒人<br />\n不過都算 我地冇理<br />\n<br />\n跟住果下先係一秒著左<br />\n有個侍應大叔特登經過我地<br />\n然後望住我地話：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">用子彈射死哂佢地（示威者）就岩喇biu biu biu</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地即刻埋單走<br />\n以後唔撚會去食<br />\n成班侍應一向都對客都西<br />\n<br />\nsor9嬲得濟唔記得影相<br />\n上網搵到佢地址<br />\n希望黃大仙竹園友咪撚去幫親<br />\n佢地平時都幾旺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7qPo0tv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7qPo0tv.png&h=d18e47b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ac7bfcba992f8c7c174a8bf57b28d6f697e45763","tid":1396952,"uid":282624,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:18:26.000Z","msg":"加入黑名單<br />\n好似有手足整咗個list"},{"pid":"04c7585dd049977ea757f695d70a46885b21f80d","tid":1396952,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:18:48.000Z","msg":"間野難食到"},{"pid":"58554fe44c8ba3beb9f899379f99cc82b9b4cbe0","tid":1396952,"uid":245644,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"update黑名單"},{"pid":"eb32494d0ec6faf85579043b1a9fcaa3b7911d01","tid":1396952,"uid":66146,"like":3,"dislike":22,"score":-19,"quote":{"pid":"b4c5aee0df57496155f37a42ef4c2c15b45ce53b","tid":1396952,"uid":296900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T09:17:40.000Z","msg":"P牌終於開到a